## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. When we do, we’ll revise the date at the bottom of this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your privacy.

**Last Updated:** October 2023

---

## Final Note

At Cats Hub, our goal is to provide helpful, trustworthy content about cats while respecting your privacy. We are committed to transparency and making sure you feel confident about how your data is handled. If you have any concerns or questions, don’t hesitate to contact us.

Thank you for trusting Cats Hub — your source for expert insights on cats!
